quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  15,1,"Alif Lam Ra. Tsino ni tsinyaali tsieshitabu nende Ikurani yinoosinjia."
  15,2,"Awundi balitsa bekomba balia bakhaya mbu, bamanyanga baba Abasalamu."
  15,3,"Baleshe sa balie ebiakhulia mana basangale, mana bakatibwe nende amekombo kobubeyi (mbu balileshelwa), ahambi ano betsa okhumanya."
  15,4,"Ne shikhwasishiakhwo olukongo lwosilwosi tawe, halali lwali nende ebise bialwo bimanyikhane."
  15,5,"Ne babulaho abandu bosibosi banyala okhuranjilila ebise biabu bieyindukho, nohomba shibanyala okhushinda tawe."
  15,6,"Ne baboola mbu; “Ewe oweshilibwa ametsulisio, toto ewe oli omulalu."
  15,7,"Shichila shina nolakhurerera Abamalaika nikali mbu ewe oli mubaboolanga obwatoto?""
  15,8,"Efwe shikhwishinjia Abamalaika tawe halali khubwatoto (ebise biokhusishibwa khwabu nibiula), ne awo shibalihebwa obwiyangu tawe (balisishibwa butswa)."
  15,9,"Toto efwe nefwe khweshia ametsulisio kano, ne khandi toto efwe nefwe khwitsa okhukalinda."
  15,10,"Ne toto khwaruma Abarumwa mumikanda chia abandu beyimbeli."
  15,11,"Ne Omurumwa yesiyesi shiyabetselanga halali bo bamukholelanga omubayo."
  15,12,"Ne endio nilwa khuyinjisinjia mumioyo chia balia abamabii."
  15,13,"Shibaisuubilanga tawe, ne bamala okhulola shingala kali khubandu bali imbeli wabu eyo."
  15,14,"Ne khubekulilanga omuliango kwomwikulu, mana baba nibaninangamwo."
  15,15,"Bakhaboolele mbu; “Toto tsimoni tsiefu tsimeesibwe, ne efwe abeene ni ababdu khulochelwe.”"